{"id": 427, "genre": 1001, "title": "戴眼镜最不能忍的是？", "description": "听说，三米开外雌雄同体，五米之外六亲不认，十米之外人畜不分，反正我不戴。", "record_count": 7466, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702200957Jjy3AVqHzKg5RN2e.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-16T12:14:25Z", "options": [{"id": 3772, "content": "一下雨，世界一片模糊", "image": null, "praise_count": 168, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124987}, {"id": 3774, "content": "当我找不到我的眼镜时我只想快点戴上眼镜找眼镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 423, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99741}, {"id": 3775, "content": "游泳时从来看不清传说中的比基尼女郎！", "image": null, "praise_count": 270, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124651}, {"id": 4064, "content": "哎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142573}, {"id": 4014, "content": "眼睛已经华丽丽的变形了（背景乐：看我七十二变）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143910}, {"id": 4284, "content": "取掉眼睛会很没安全感，感觉整个世界遍布危险。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145740}, {"id": 3871, "content": "踢球打球经常被眼镜上的汗水蒙蔽了双眼或经常被击落。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103895}, {"id": 3872, "content": "化了眼妆基本看不见，而且睫毛膏会粘到眼镜上", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143113}, {"id": 4098, "content": "特别是跑步的时候加戴个耳机，怎么喊都不应", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 62073}, {"id": 4089, "content": "不近视不带眼镜只带墨镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130521}, {"id": 3801, "content": "看3D电影得带两个", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142662}, {"id": 3802, "content": "太阳眼镜戴不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136761}, {"id": 3803, "content": "如果黑框的容易不辨雌雄", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114688}, {"id": 3804, "content": "接吻", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234813Jz5afF8i0X6kyhoj.jpg", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142689}, {"id": 3808, "content": "尤其夏天 带久了 镜框油腻的不得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 108, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3809, "content": "老是模糊要擦，很麻烦！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 93731}, {"id": 3810, "content": "只要一脱下眼光呆滞像斗鸡眼似的 还好我没近视", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3812, "content": "怕影响下一代，不能找同样戴眼镜的", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115353}, {"id": 3959, "content": "10个眼镜9个坏，剩下一个是变态…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3960, "content": "有熊猫眼，和熊猫相反", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143536}, {"id": 3962, "content": "游泳", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 106459}, {"id": 4071, "content": "眼镜脏了是一个世界，擦了眼镜之后就是一个另一个世界，摘了眼镜又是一个世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144289}, {"id": 4875, "content": "下雨眼镜没有自带雨刷", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147582}, {"id": 5984, "content": "永远都有人说你还是不戴眼镜好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 95452}, {"id": 7425, "content": "每天起床眼镜总会莫名消失:D", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155952}, {"id": 3844, "content": "不带眼镜的时候 别人说你还是带眼镜比较好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131812}, {"id": 7684, "content": "眼镜突然忘了放在哪，根本找不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125977}, {"id": 4102, "content": "夏天从空调房间突然走到高温的室外，瞬间一片雾气～真尴尬～", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144610}, {"id": 4104, "content": "配眼镜看不到带眼镜框的样子。离得太近又看不全。根本无法看到配镜片前的样子！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144646}, {"id": 3856, "content": "用单反无法100%看到取景框里的画面", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142977}, {"id": 3857, "content": "镜片会磨损啊一两年就旧了要换新的又是一笔钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133480}, {"id": 4113, "content": "戴眼镜再戴夹头式耳机，感觉整个脑袋都被挤变形了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4114, "content": "我不理解戴眼镜什么感觉?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 53650}, {"id": 188178, "content": "眼镜形状没选好整个人都不好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357934}, {"id": 3859, "content": "啪啪啪时，戴了别扭，不戴看不清", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116854}, {"id": 3862, "content": "篮球是眼镜毁灭者", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142662}, {"id": 13079, "content": "眼睛会变小", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201385}, {"id": 3864, "content": "最不能忍的是，明明眼镜是矫正视力的，而近视却越来越严重了,戴了第一副就会有第二幅.", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140604}, {"id": 3865, "content": "不好接吻那个其实是来拉仇恨的吗…", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135713}, {"id": 3866, "content": "戴眼镜眼睛变形，度数增加快！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142732}, {"id": 3867, "content": "夏天一出汗  镜片就起雾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143047}, {"id": 3868, "content": "一直还是单身狗。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143060}, {"id": 13347, "content": "太阳晒太久会有印留在脸的两边 好久才能白回来啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202465}, {"id": 4137, "content": "美化见到的一切。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145135}, {"id": 3885, "content": "丑爆了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143256}, {"id": 7215, "content": "前方朋友一片海\n而我面无表情穿过它\n都说 太高冷\n我只想说 看不清 认识？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154946}, {"id": 3927, "content": "摘下眼镜，别人认不出我了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143352}, {"id": 6488, "content": "被打脸的时候会掉，然后这架就没法吵了，挂在脸上很尴尬，还会笑场。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147548}, {"id": 6234, "content": "购物双手提东西没法扶正滑下来的眼镜。。只好把脸上仰斜眼走路。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150238}, {"id": 3941, "content": "跑步时因为流汗滑下来，因为太热有雾气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143421}]}